&lt;p data-start=&quot;87&quot; data-end=&quot;172&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;General Manager (General Manager in Training)&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Cool Willy&#39;s Air Conditioning &amp;amp; Plumbing | Tucson, AZ&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Lead Today. Take Over Tomorrow.&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Cool Willy&#39;s Air Conditioning &amp;amp; Plumbing is seeking an experienced &lt;strong&gt;Home Services General Manager&lt;/strong&gt; to work alongside our current General Manager before transitioning into full leadership of our Tucson operation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a unique opportunity for a proven leader who wants a structured succession plan rather than being thrown into a role on day one. You&#39;ll spend time learning our people, processes, culture, and operations before taking full ownership of a &lt;strong&gt;$10 million residential HVAC and Plumbing business&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you&#39;ve successfully led a high-performing home service company and know how to drive revenue, develop leaders, improve profitability, and build winning teams, we want to talk with you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;During the Transition&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Partner directly with the current General Manager to learn all aspects of the business.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Build relationships with employees, managers, and key customers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Gain a deep understanding of company operations, financials, and culture.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Identify opportunities to improve efficiency and profitability.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;After Transition&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Assume full responsibility for the daily operations of the Tucson branch.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lead HVAC, Plumbing, Customer Service, Dispatch, Sales, and Installation teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Own the branch P&amp;amp;L and drive revenue, profitability, and EBITDA growth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Develop department managers through coaching, accountability, and leadership.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Monitor and improve key performance indicators, including:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Revenue&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Gross Margin&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;EBITDA&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Average Ticket&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Membership Growth&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Close Rates&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Customer Satisfaction&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Employee Retention&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Create a culture built on accountability, teamwork, and exceptional customer service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Partner with recruiting to attract and retain top talent.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Qualifications&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5+ years of General Manager or senior operational leadership experience within the residential home services industry.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience managing a &lt;strong&gt;$5–6 million or larger HVAC, Plumbing, Electrical, or multi-trade home service operation.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Strong understanding of residential service, sales, installation, dispatch, and customer service operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Proven experience managing a branch P&amp;amp;L and improving profitability.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Demonstrated ability to coach and develop managers and field leaders.&lt;/

